verbose_text: Assessment of exercise intolerance by bicycle ergometry confirmed premature fatigue and an increased level of plasma lactate (basic lactate : 6.1 and 19.1 mmol/L after exercise, normal : 0.5-2.2 mmol/L) and CPK (basic CPK : 386 and 566 U/L after exercise, normal : 38-174 U/L).
